{"tid":1682431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華運載火箭 突中止發射","createTime":"2019-10-30T04:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T06:13:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"880d502a39097ac05939ecbcc14506cf2b72de15","tid":1682431,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191029/CPOANFDH4OQWT4FAFSJWGLYKGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191029%2FCPOANFDH4OQWT4FAFSJWGLYKGM%2F&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt38pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b904e039\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191029%2FCPOANFDH4OQWT4FAFSJWGLYKGM%2F&h=50248f69\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191029/CPOANFDH4OQWT4FAFSJWGLYKGM/</a><br />\n<br />\n華運載火箭 突中止發射<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/BwEvZn-kS93e8HatOPIVyogZBzU=/802x915/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/VVX7HYT3UF5EVBPYVHIFE3RZR4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FBwEvZn-kS93e8HatOPIVyogZBzU%3D%2F802x915%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FVVX7HYT3UF5EVBPYVHIFE3RZR4.gif&h=69b1fabb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地航天發射再遇挫。中國航天科工集團研製的「快舟一號甲」運載火箭（圖），原定昨天中午在甘肅酒泉衞星發射中心發射，但事前突然宣佈計劃「因故中止」。央視等官媒卻提前用大字標題報道火箭成功發射，之後才陸續刪除，情況尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官媒預賀擺烏龍<br />\n<br />\n快舟一號甲固體運載火箭原定昨天11時45分，攜帶吉林一號高分02A衞星在酒泉發射升空。不過發射前突然宣佈「計劃因故中止」，原因未明，央視、微博等現場直播亦宣告終止。惟令人尷尬的是，官媒央視國際頻道、吉林網等媒體仍一度提前以「成功發射 『吉林一號』高分02A星」為題，報道「衞星順利進入預定軌道，發射任務取得圓滿成功」的內容。文中更詳細介紹了該衞星的設計、功能，以及擁有的創新技術，之後才陸續刪除。<br />\n<br />\n本次發射是快舟一號甲今年第二次執行商業任務。該火箭屬於小型固體運載火箭，2017年初首次發射，現主要為低軌小衞星提供發射服務。據統計，中國2019年至今最少16次航天發射，其中除今次發射出現異常外，另有三次發射被確認失敗。今年8月發射長征三號乙運載火箭，雖然成功將中星18號衞星發射升空，但出現衞星工作異常情況。3月發射靈鵲一號B星，因火箭一二級分離後姿態失穩，發射失敗。<br />\n<br />\n央視/微博"},{"pid":"cc0f693723f59a9c6e299ca7acc5179d8cecb815","tid":1682431,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc8536k.jpg&h=6d7fb408&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7e14b8857a16c5d3177291c419a76b8a522d968b","tid":1682431,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">已經有13個英美參議員/單位就GPhone出聲<br />\n快啲Rt and like and reply哂佢<br />\n全部響哂 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">/Task1</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt38pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=1d6b395f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"e248a9a15bdda1e6b34e52ff6596a8524e8a9e12","tid":1682431,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"鳩都未硬就射哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e024b7640cd3bcb3b5e587910ec7906fe24366a0","tid":1682431,"uid":66547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"大陸新聞比事件早出街唔係第一次出現。<br />\n砍差佬案都係未砍就出新聞"},{"pid":"442bd0db59d70f09437e3d192a4422620b481424","tid":1682431,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e024b7640cd3bcb3b5e587910ec7906fe24366a0","tid":1682431,"uid":66547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"大陸新聞比事件早出街唔係第一次出現。<br />\n砍差佬案都係未砍就出新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"